<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-12-08T11:10:33-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-12-08T11:10:33-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T11:10:33-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/a9DFjTwteBiMbEI8chPLU5J-fiw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72838629/236830_MAIN_Gift_Guide_LEDE_STILL_CVir吉尼亚.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;一系列伟大的科技和非科技礼物，旨在送给我们所有人中的修补匠、创意者和孩子。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>边缘员工</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T10:44:51-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T10:44:51-05:00</updated><title>菲律宾的“人工智能”快餐店大多只是人类工人</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示机器人执行多种功能的图形&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xtmKR3v3jncqd9daqSFqolp9l7Q=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/72943984/acastro_200730_1777_ai_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Alex Castro / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;cvSLdd&quot;>;人工智能驱动的得来速公司 Presto Automation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20230330005316/en/Presto-Promotes-Dan-Mosher-to-President-and-Xavier-Casanova-to-Chief-Operating- Office 将自己描述为“业内最大的劳动力自动化技术提供商之一”，并吹嘘其有能力增加销售额并“节省”人类劳动时间。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;AB6mv2&quot;>;但是根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sec.gov/ix?doc=/Archives/edgar/data/1822145/000121390023089293/ea188717-8k_presto.htm &quot;>;最近向美国证券交易委员会提交的文件&lt;/a>;显示，场外员工正在介入并完成了超过 70% 的订单。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Gvd8T9&quot;>;尽管公司的品牌和营销工作有所改善Presto Automation 提出了神奇的驾车技术，在菲律宾等地使用工人，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/ai-fast-food-drive- thrus-need- human-workers-70-of-time&quot;>;根据&lt;em>;彭博社&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。 AI得来速技术被全国各地的Carl&#39;s Jr.、Hardee&#39;s、Del Taco、Checkers等快餐店采用，有望降低劳动力成本并增加...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993427/artificial-intelligence-presto-automation-fast-food-drive-thru-philippines-workers&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993427/artificial-intelligence-presto-automation-fast-food-drive-thru-philippines-workers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993427/artificial-intelligence-presto-automation-fast-food-drive-thru-philippines-workers</id><author><name>佐藤米亚</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T10:31:50-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T10:31:50-05:00</updated><title>谷歌的人工智能笔记应用程序现已向美国用户开放</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 徽标和黑色漩涡&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tN_8mxkyZ3O4fTgahz4l-nQZ188=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72943947/STK093_Google_05.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;aoPDtF&quot;>;NotebookLM，Google 的实验性人工智能笔记应用，现已在美国广泛使用。它还获得了&lt;a href=&quot;https://support.google.com/notebooklm/answer/14290935?hl=en&amp;amp;ref_topic=14287611&amp;amp;sjid=10374133267015279073-NC&quot;>;多项新功能&lt;/a>;，并且正在“开始”使用 Google 的 Gemini Pro AI 模型“帮助文档理解和推理”，&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.google/technology/ai/notebooklm-new-features-availability/&quot;>;根据该公司的说法&lt; /a>;.&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1Dx45W&quot;>;NotebookLM 已经可以执行一些操作，例如总结导入到应用程序中的文档、提出要点，甚至回答有关笔记来源的问题。但现在，谷歌还添加了一种将笔记转换为其他类型文档的方法。选择要包含的所有笔记后，NotebookLM 将自动建议格式，例如大纲或学习指南。不过，Google 指出，您还可以告诉 NotebookLM 转换您的笔记...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993441/google-notebooklm -available-gemini-pro&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993441/google-notebooklm-available-gemini-pro" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993441/google-notebooklm-available-gemini-pro</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T10:30:04-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T10:30:04-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年儿童节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BuamjMoqrNyuzYDmwJ1sITdned8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72888273/236830_FOR_KIDS_Gift_Guide_Art_CVirgin ia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;让我们帮助您为各种孩子找到各种礼物。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23964428/kids-teens-gifts-unique-ideas-2023-presents-children-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23964428/kids-teens-gifts-unique-ideas-2023-presents-children-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23964428/kids-teens-gifts-unique-ideas-2023-presents-children-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T09:30:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T09:30:00-05:00</updated><title>清理半导体有毒遗产的斗争</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;3D 插图显示半导体工厂渗出有毒污泥。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_-nAiCYG03PKQmPIr5qH6pnglMs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72941881/236836_Infrastruction_SILICON_FABS_Sisi_Kim .0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Sisi Kim 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;总统乔·拜登承诺重振美国制造业。硅谷的长期居民希望危险化学品不会随之回来。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23990525/semiconductor-biden-infrastruct-plan-toxic-化学品&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23990525/semiconductor-biden-infrastructure-plan-toxic-chemicals" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23990525/semiconductor-biden-infrastruct-plan-有毒-化学品</id><author><name>贾斯汀·卡尔玛</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>需要建造房屋以提供更好的互联网</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;微型样板房的 3D 插图，侧面刻有 Wi-Fi 符号。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/V8ic-bOkWRSamCPOYSzxxZPvQKk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72941880/236836_Infrastruction_HOMEBUILT_INTERNET_Sisi_Kim .jpg.0。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Sisi Kim 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;许多房屋正在建设中，但由于缺乏对互联网基础设施的了解以及削减成本的需要，这意味着他们需要互联网糟透了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23991092/homes-need-to-be-built-for-better-internet &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23991092/homes-need-to-be-built-for-better-internet" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23991092/homes-need-to-be-built-for-better-internet</id><author><name>乔安娜·内利厄斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T08:30:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T08:30:00-05:00</updated><title>宫崎骏的《男孩与苍鹭》是一个美丽的遗迹——也是一个时代的结束</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;动画电影《男孩与苍鹭》中的静态图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rftEHrwE0CReUIJF7PQbWErUJ-o=/117x0:1283x777/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72459128/F3gcKFQWsAAboPZ.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：吉卜力工作室&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;吉卜力工作室的最新电影继今年早些时候在日本首映后，现已在北美影院上映。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23797349/how-do-you-live-review-studio-ghibli-hayao-miyazaki&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23797349/how-do-you-live-review-studio-ghibli-hayao-miyazaki" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23797349/how-do-you-live-review-studio-ghibli-hayao-miyazaki</id><author><name>艾丽西娅·哈迪克</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T08:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T08:00:00-05:00</updated><title>为什么埃隆·马斯克的 Grok 聊天机器人如此无趣？</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Elon Musk 带问号壁纸&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lBq4qNMzSSXfxIGEmo5Nv6-d00k=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/72943386/STK171_VRG_Illo_15_Normand_ElonMusk_15.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;你相信这个人会讲一个好笑话吗？&lt;/em>; |插图由 Laura Normand / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uhVJ9P&quot;>;很好。让我们来谈谈 xAI，它获得的资金高达 10 亿美元或无论如何&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tcfrV1&quot;>;xAI，根据一些评论员的说法，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/2023/12/06/elon-musk -twitter-x-ai-funding&quot;>;埃隆·马斯克“拯救 X”的努力，该平台更广为人知的名字是 Twitter。人们认为，马斯克可能已经与广告商进行了惊人的打击，但未能通过订阅来弥补缺口，但他可以通过目前仅适用于一小部分蓝色支票的新人工智能产品的炒作来筹集资金。该产品就是 Grok：一款 ChatGPT 风格的应答机器人，据称具有幽默感。这引发了几个问题，特别是因为人工智能聊天机器人仍然是一个盈利途径不确定的资金坑。但有一个问题让我很困惑：为什么 Grok 这么无趣？ &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;E3tGkj&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.ai/&quot;>;xAI 网站&lt;/a>;清楚地表明 Grok 的启动方式很奇怪......&lt;/p>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23992489/xai-musk-grok-humor-chatbot&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23992489/xai-musk-grok-humor-chatbot" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23992489/xai-musk-grok-humor-chatbot</id><author><name>伊丽莎白·洛帕托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-08T05:07:06-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-08T05:07:06-05:00</updated><title>在 Google 审核调整后，YouTube 用户现在可以暂停评论</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手机上的四张屏幕截图，描绘了 YouTube 用于评论审核的新暂停选项。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IlcK_c-8IwkanGBpWgg4mct84AY=/0x10:1920x1290/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72943133/YouTube_Comment_Moderation_Tools.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;YouTube 的新评论审核功能可让您在不删除现有视频评论的情况下暂时离开评论者。&lt;/em>; |图片：YouTube&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;PcGzZY&quot;>;YouTube 为创作者推出了一款新的审核工具，允许他们暂停评论，防止任何新评论添加到视频中，同时保留已添加的评论已发布。 YouTube 在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkRfArvrzheW2E7b6SVT7vQ/community?lb=UgkxP6pziafkHJ4fyaHxfK38vNh5mtk6oYoM&quot;>;周四发布的博文&lt;/a>;中表示，该功能使创作者能够“从管理评论，如果评论变得势不可挡”，并为评论的管理方式提供了一定的灵活性。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;t6Sflj&quot;>;在此更新之前，YouTube 创作者只有两个选项来审核评论，否则评论将完全免费- for-all：要么在发布评论之前保留评论以进行手动审核，要么完全禁用视频上的&lt;em>;所有&lt;/em>;评论。 YouTube 表示暂停功能现已推出 - 我们已要求该公司...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993284/ youtube-pause-comment-moderation-feature-announcement&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993284/youtube-pause-comment-moderation-feature-announcement" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/8/23993284/youtube-pause-comment-moderation-feature-announcement</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-07T23:32:21-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-07T23:32:21-05:00</updated><title>杰夫·基斯利 (Geoff Keighley) 让视频游戏开发商失望了</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2019 游戏大奖 - 展示&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/O7wJg_scVgU2Fu8-ZTSZglOoU2s=/0x0:4095x2730/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/72942758/1193629349.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：JC Olivera / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;q6h9fJ&quot;>;此时，你无法谈论如何2023 年令人惊叹的是今年发布的游戏质量，更不用说 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23977673/bytedance-nuverse-gaming-layoffs-restruct&quot;>;这是&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23951138/ubisoft-montreal-layoffs-hybride-assassins-creed&quot;>;已经&lt;/a>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/28/23894266/epic-games-layoffs-fortnite-unreal-engine&quot;>;完全&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2023/10/30/23938990/bungie-sony-layoffs-delays-destiny-final-shape-marathon&quot;>;对于制作它们的人来说是灾难性的&lt;/a>;。但这正是 Geoff Keighley 在今年的游戏奖中所做的。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;lBQox4&quot;>;数字各不相同，但估计介于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gamesindustry.biz/over -6000-games-industry-jobs-lost-in-2023-so-far&quot;>;仅今年就有六七千名工人失业&lt;/a>;。任何级别的工作室规模或成功都未能幸免。而那些被解雇的人现在被迫争夺数量不断减少的空缺职位。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;JD3ajN&quot;>;“这是过去 15 年来游戏行业最动荡的时期之一，”国际游戏开发者协会执行董事 Jakin Vela 说道，&lt;a href= “https://www.polygon.com/23964448/video-game-industry-layoffs-crisis-2023&quot;>;在...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/23992402/geoff-keighley-the-game-awards-layoffs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23992402/geoff-keighley-the-game-awards-layoffs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23992402/geoff-keighley-the-game-awards-layoffs</id><author><name>阿什·帕里什</name></author></entry></feed>